ny_4 = 1.3375 + (0.16975 + 2*0.18821875 + 2*0.18834375 + 0.2115) / 6 = 1.515625\n\nSo, the estimated value of y(0.4) using the 4th order Runge-Kutta method with step size h = 0.1 is y_4 = 1.515625."
